languages.text: "Обычно в гадюшниках запрещенку и прячут, думают, в грязь не полезет никто. Давай ищи, если план по конфискату не выполним, Френзо с нас шкуру спустит".

languages.text: «Suelen esconder contrabando en lugares asquerosos, se creen que nadie va a rebuscar entre la mugre. Como no cumplamos con el cupo de bienes confiscados, Frensoe nos va a reventar».

languages.text: 「誰も汚物をかき分けようとはしない。もし我々が押収ノルマを達成しなければ、フレンソーは我々の隠れ場所を見つけるだろう」
languages.original_text: "They usually hide contraband in disgusting places, thinking no one's going to wade through the filth. If we don't meet our confiscation quotas, Frensoe will have our hides."

languages.text: “那些家伙通常会把违禁品藏在令人作呕的地方，以为没人会蹚着屎尿过去查。可他们不知道，要是我们没收的违禁品达不到定额，弗伦索会扒了我们的皮。”
languages.original_text: "They usually hide contraband in disgusting places, thinking no one's going to wade through the filth. If we don't meet our confiscation quotas, Frensoe will have our hides."

languages.text: "Sie verstecken Schmuggelgut für gewöhnlich an abstoßenden Orten, weil sie denken, dass niemand durch den Dreck watet. Aber wenn wir unser Konfiszierungssoll nicht erfüllen, reißt uns Frensoe den Arsch auf."
languages.original_text: "They usually hide contraband in disgusting places, thinking no one's going to wade through the filth. If we don't meet our confiscation quotas, Frensoe will have our hides."

languages.text: « D'habitude, ils planquent leur contrebande dans des recoins répugnants, dans l'espoir que personne ne vienne mettre les mains dans la crasse. Si on remplit pas les quotas de confiscation, Frensoe va nous faire la peau. »

languages.text: "Yasa dışı ürünleri genellikle iğrenç yerlerde saklarlar. O pisliğin içinden kimsenin geçmeyeceğini düşünürler. Ele geçirme kotamızı doldurmazsak Frensoe bizi diri diri yüzer."
